motion-detection-python/
│
├── motion_detection.py        # Main Python script containing the motion detection logic
├── background_subtraction.py  # (Optional) Module handling background modeling
├── utils.py                   # Helper functions for masking, contour detection, etc.
│
├── assets/
│   ├── sample_frame.jpg       # Example frame or captured image
│   ├── README_image.jpg       # Image used in documentation
│   └── icon.png               # App icon or UI resources (if any)
│
├── data/
│   ├── logs.txt               # Stores motion timestamps (if logging enabled)
│   └── config.json            # Configuration file for thresholds/settings
│
├── screenshots/
│   └── occupied.jpg           # Demo image (uploaded file)
│
├── README.md                  # Documentation for the project
└── requirements.txt           # List of Python dependencies
